        <item>
            <title>小米 SU7 Ultra 挑战速度极限，时速 359.71 公里刷新全球四门量产车纪录</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/17/su7-ultra/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=su7-ultra</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/17/su7-ultra/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 10:00:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米 SU7 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275570</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米汽车近日宣布，其首款量产电动车小米 SU7 Ultra 创下了每小时 359.71 公里的惊人速度纪录，远超高铁的营运速度，成为全球最快的四门量产车之一。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111734633.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275576 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111734633-546x580.jpg" alt="" width="546" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111734633-546x580.jpg 546w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111734633.jpg 848w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 546px" /></a></p><p>小米 SU7 Ultra 性能引人注目，其搭载三电机系统，总输出功率高达 1548 匹马力，0 至 100 公里每小时的加速仅需 1.98 秒。在设计上，SU7 Ultra 结合碳纤维材料的车顶与侧裙，以及具有运动感的菱形进气口，进一步提升车辆的空气动力学性能，为极速行驶提供稳定支援。</p><p>小米采用由宁德时代提供的高功率电池，峰值电压高达 897 伏特，即使电量仅剩 20%，仍能释放超过 800 千瓦的放电功率，并支持最高 5.2C 的充电倍率，10% 至 80% 的充电时间仅需 11 分钟，让日常使用更具便利性。</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">虽然小米 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">SU7 Ultra </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">售价高昂，不过 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">10 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">分钟内获得了 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">3680 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">台的小额订金，追求极限的中国用户对小米 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">SU7 Ultra 仍</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">相当看好。</span></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.163.com/dy/article/JH1VQAD20511DG68.html">网易</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
